     + Methods ToolTipAutoPopTime, ToolTipInitialTime, ToolTipResetDelays,
       ToolTipReshowTime, ToolTipIcon and ToolTipTitle.
     * Methods ToolTipWidth and ToolTipMultiLine are now defined as BLOCK.
